Revision history for Padre-Plugin-Alarm

0.14   2010.12.06
	- Restored missing POT/PO translation sources (Damyan Ivanov, AZAWAWI)

0.13   2010.10.28
	- Removed Test::NeedsDisplay dependency (AZAWAWI)

0.11   2010.10.28
	- Fixed Test::NeedsDisplay dependency in [LoadTests] and [CompileTests] uses now
	  both no_display and needs_display (AZAWAWI)

0.10   2010.10.27
	- t/00-load.t is magically injected by [@PadrePlugin] via [LoadTests] (AZAWAWI)

0.09   2010.10.22
	- Switched to Dist::Zilla (AZAWAWI)
	- Fixed 00-load.t failure when $ENV{DISPLAY} is not set (AZAWAWI)
	- Fixed RT #53691 for Padre-Plugin-Alarm: More events when timer reached (AZAWAWI)
	- The alarm is also more accurate than before (AZAWAWI)
	- Added an alarm wave sample that is licensed under Creative Commons Creative Commons
	  Sampling Plus 1.0 (GETTY)

0.08  2010.10.19
	- Renamed to the new Padre 0.43 PO naming scheme (AZAWAWI)
	- Fixed RT #61653: Plugin not compatible with Padre 0.70 (AZAWAWI)
	- Translation files are now copied to share folder using Module::Build's share_dir (AZAWAWI)

0.07  2009.05.31
    - Removed taint mode for test, which lead to some failures (JQUELIN)

0.06  2009.05.26
	- Add Chinese (Traditional) translation (BLUET).
	- Added Arabic translation (AZAWAWI).
	- Added Spanish translation (BRUNOV).

0.05  2009.05.18
	- Added translations:
		- Brazilian Portuguese (GARU)
		- French (JQUELIN)
		- Polish (THEREK)
		- Chinese Simpified (FAYLAND)

0.04  2009.02.03
	- Fix http://www.nntp.perl.org/group/perl.cpan.testers/2009/02/msg3185057.html

0.03  2009.02.01
	- Compatibility with Padre 0.26

0.02  2008.12.08
	- Fix clear_alarm

0.01  Date/time
	- First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

